OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FFew of us will know quite what it's
OL,7,Flike to experience the savage murder
OL,8,Fof a close family member and then to
OL,9,Frelive the horror day after day in
OL,10,Fnews reports and then in a judicial
OL,11,Ffight for answers.
OL,13,FBut that is the burden that Katie
OL,14,FAmess, daughter of the late Sir David
OL,15,FAmess, cannot escape.
