OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FI've just interviewed her in St
OL,7,FPeter's Catholic church on the
OL,8,Foutskirts of Southend. This is the
OL,9,Fseaside town - now a city thanks to
OL,10,FAmess's tireless campaigning - that he
OL,11,Frepresented as a much-loved MP for 24
OL,12,Fyears, till he was assassinated by Ali
OL,13,FHarbi Ali on October 15, 2021, in an
OL,14,Fact of terrorism carried out in the
OL,15,Fname of Islamic State.
