OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FWhat Katie and her mum Julia want is
OL,7,Fvery simple and would seem to most of
OL,8,Fus a basic human right, especially
OL,9,Fafter the trauma they live with: an
OL,10,Finquest, to establish why police and
OL,11,Fsecurity services did not protect her
OL,12,Ffather.
OL,14,FThis is no self-indulgent "if only"
OL,15,Fquestion. The point is that Ali was
OL,16,Fidentified as someone at risk of
OL,17,Fbecoming a dangerous extremist, a
OL,18,Fpotential terrorist, in 2015, and was
OL,19,Fenrolled on the government's Prevent
OL,20,Fprogramme.
