OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FPrevent is supposed to wean vulnerable
OL,7,Fpeople off extremism ideology and to
OL,8,Fkeep track of them.
OL,10,FAli however was on the programme for
OL,11,Fjust a year. And after he was removed
OL,12,Ffrom it, he worked day after day as a
OL,13,Flone wolf terrorist, to identify a
OL,14,FBritish MP to slay.
OL,16,FHe plotted for years to obtain what he
OL,17,Fsaw as just punishment for the UK's
OL,18,Fair strikes on Islamic State in
OL,19,FSeptember 2014.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
