OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FAmess appears to have been chosen
OL,7,Fbecause he had less protection than -
OL,8,Ffor example, the former cabinet
OL,9,Fminister Michael Gove, whom Ali also
OL,10,Fplanned to kill.
OL,12,FWhat Katie wants to know is why
OL,13,Fprecisely MI5 and counter terrorism
OL,14,Fpolice seemingly ceased taking an
OL,15,Finterest in Ali after 2016, even
OL,16,Fthough that is when his terrorist
OL,17,Fpreparations only started in earnest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
