OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FThey also feel let down by Essex
OL,7,Fpolice, whom were contacted by Katie
OL,8,FAmess's brother, also called David,
OL,9,Fabout a threat made to him and his
OL,10,Ffather.
OL,12,FThis threat was unconnected to Ali,
OL,13,Fbut Katie believes this should have
OL,14,Fled the police to automatically send
OL,15,Fofficers to Sir David's surgery the
OL,16,Ffollowing day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
