OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FKatie and her mother Julia would
OL,7,Fobviously benefit from understanding
OL,8,Fhow and why their father was - in
OL,9,Ftheir view - let down by the
OL,10,Finstitutions of the state. But she
OL,11,Falso believes that the family of Ali,
OL,12,Fwhose lives have also been wrecked,
OL,13,Fdeserve respect and answers too.
OL,15,FAnd she fears MPs are all more
OL,16,Fvulnerable in the absence of a
OL,17,Fforensic inquiry into what went wrong.
