OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FAn inquest was originally opened by
OL,7,Fthe coroner Lincoln Brookes on 27
OL,8,FOctober 2021. But it was then
OL,9,Fadjourned until Ali was convicted of
OL,10,Fmurder in April 2022.
OL,12,FBrookes considered whether it should
OL,13,Fbe resumed. He consulted the family
OL,14,Fwho were in shock, partly because Sir
OL,15,FDavid's wife had just suffered a
OL,16,Fstroke.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
