OL,3,CWhy the family of murdered MP Sir
OL,4,CDavid Amess deserve answers
OL,6,FThey feared the inquest would add to
OL,7,Ftheir stress and said they did not
OL,8,Fwant that. It was only later they
OL,9,Flearned an inquest was their only
OL,10,Froute to the knowledge they so
OL,11,Fdesperately desired.
OL,13,FSince then they have been campaigning
OL,14,Fto persuade Brookes to open it again.
OL,15,FIn July he decided against doing so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
